&lt;h4 id=&quot;for-a-local-deployment-of-the-documentation-project-jekyll--mmistakes-template&quot;&gt;For a local deployment of the documentation project (Jekyll + MMistakes template)&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Install ruby, Jekyll&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-bash highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;brew install ruby
gem install jekyll
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Install setup (given the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Gemfile&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Gemfile.lock&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;_config.yml&lt;/code&gt; files)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

